* Support for Login Items, /Library/StartupItems and
  LoginHooks, see https://apple.stackexchange.com/a/451942
  [2026-02-08].
* Use an actual configuration file in /usr/local/etc or
  /opt/etc (is that correct for Apple Silicon?) [2026-02-08].
* Move to zsh or sh, the latter for retaining compatibility
  with older Macs [2026-02-08].
* Is using the Trash in the one edge case where a launch agent
  is within the user's Library folder a little confusing? 
  [2026-02-08]